::Battera:: 

She ran to the entrance.  "OH, can't those preds just go and blow 
themselves up?!" She then looked at her arm. "Well most of them." 
She  transformed into bat mode and flew upward.  She fired her optic 
lazars on Injector. "GO AWAY!" she yelled at him. "GO AND LEAVE US 
ALONE!" she fired again.
